{"tid":1121710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斯里蘭卡連環爆炸 伊斯蘭國IS承認責任","createTime":"2019-04-23T13:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T16:41:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6a43c9c83079dea5365996463d2cf05368a90b","tid":1121710,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭國(IS)今天(23日)透過旗下的宣傳機構阿瑪克通訊社(Amaq)，宣稱斯里蘭卡21日發生的連環爆炸恐攻事件是旗下戰士所為。<br />\n<br />\n阿瑪克通訊社發布的聲明指出：「那些前天針對美國領導的聯盟，以及斯里蘭卡的基督徒發動攻擊的人，都是伊斯蘭國組織的戰士。」<br />\n<br />\n但是路透社指出，伊斯蘭國並未對他們發動斯里蘭卡恐攻，提供相關佐證。<br />\n<br />\n斯里蘭卡的教堂與高檔酒店21日遭到8起連環爆炸攻擊，造成至今已知321人喪生，大約500人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在伊斯蘭國宣稱發動斯里蘭卡連環爆炸攻擊之前，斯里蘭卡政府今天稍早引述警方的初步調查報告指出，這起連環炸彈攻擊是為了報復3月中旬，紐西蘭基督城(Christchurch)2座清真寺遭到白人至上主義者攻擊的事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2018540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2018540&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=31b79cc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2018540</a>"},{"pid":"b1915871440f02b1b061644dddd683c0ee55d359","tid":1121710,"uid":193642,"like":214,"dislike":0,"score":214,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"isis依d過氣組織仲夠膽出嚟認屎認屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1ffe7da253dc7866461d739c30c07669721861","tid":1121710,"uid":2230,"like":188,"dislike":0,"score":188,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"Isis見冇人認諗住認左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa9052122295ad97802be190fc15cd3b5de6ca4","tid":1121710,"uid":46245,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"quote":{"pid":"5d1ffe7da253dc7866461d739c30c07669721861","tid":1121710,"uid":2230,"like":188,"dislike":0,"score":188,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"Isis見冇人認諗住認左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"Isis:我捱義氣頂左佢，算夠雷氣啦<i