":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"436fb7d5f29a5f636b5712ba182ba4c263e2a3e5","tid":1121710,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9164e9a349c373e1fc047994eb2c16cc05b544a9","tid":1121710,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b27bc9ca260d644e5906861872a95d7a9505b95a","tid":1121710,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:52:54.000Z","msg":"耶撚只係起教堂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T01:08:08.000Z","msg":"傳下教、派下食物引人信?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T01:13:37.000Z","msg":"你識條鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T01:26:19.000Z","msg":"我聽過話喺第三世界<br />\n信咗耶就好快得到食物<br />\n唔信就要排幾個鐘<br />\n但啲耶教救援組織接受捐款又唔介意不信者異教徒甚至回教徒捐錢"},{"pid":"c3b9814ee1d6b7d26d253bb5551b2f586cc33a06","tid":1121710,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f45edde93470463ad59b2964c07f9229e0fef4ce","tid":1121710,"uid":164980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:37:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T01:30:35.000Z","msg":"應該唔洗出手喇，都會自然解散"},{"pid":"3f866d04e0f3c84bd00cb1228a8d14c23239cd3e","tid":1121710,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T01:35:00.000Z","msg":"唔係好明承認責任意思，係咪佢地會賠償畀受害者？點解唔係用承認策劃呢？"},{"pid":"a9888cb3071c8c66725c83d1e5db0a0ba7a09407","tid":1121710,"uid":17506,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"3b313cee37742e1adb1caba12ca6a4562dd1a0df","tid":1121710,"uid":84128,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:12:16.000Z","msg":"喂不如去搞下中共先啦<br />\n人地搞你咁多同胞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T01:44:58.000Z","msg":"拉登生前曾經說：「中國是全球唯一絕對不能惹的國家！」<br />\n<br />\n原因是這樣的：<br />\n<br />\n基地組織曾派出八名恐怖分子襲擊中國，結果如下：<br />\n<br />\n1）一人在炸北京西直門立體交通橋時，在橋上迷了路；<br />\n<br />\n2）一人在上海坐公車自殺炸彈時，擠了兩小時沒擠上車​​；<br />\n<br />\n3）一人在武漢炸超市時，炸彈遙控器被偷；<br />\n<br />\n4）一人在炸成都政府大樓時，在門口被保安當作疆獨份子逮捕、狂揍、逼供；<br />\n<br />\n5）一人成功地在河北炸礦，死傷數百人，潛回基地組織後，半年都沒見任何到有关的新聞報導，遂被組織以&quot;謊報戰果罪&quot;報處決了（這個最可憐！）；<br />\n<br />\n6）一人曾經嘗試炸廣州，結果剛一出火車站，炸藥包就給飛車黨搶了；<br />\n<br />\n7）一人剛到西安就失聯，後來在醫院找到人，但卻是在昏迷當中，醫生說他不但吃到黑心食品，還喝到假酒，可能會成為植物人；<br />\n<br />\n8）後來，賓拉登改派一名女恐怖分子去炸海南島，結果竟然被騙去賣淫；<br />\n<br />\n最後，賓拉登不得不說：「記得！中國是全球唯一絕對不能惹的國家！」"},{"pid":"daf3eb26915631059df23dbab203be85c4ef427f","tid":1121710,"uid":3297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdabff7fbf92478b5b679ecb94baf3fc67acea50","tid":1121710,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"其實點解要認？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:26:42.000Z","msg":"幫其他組織掩飾"},{"pid":"cd4644a268b9a05a8443c2436a1ae97df938e1fc","tid":1121710,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:39:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be483ad289cbe509397870b65b16080247218cd8","tid":1121710,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daf3eb26915631059df23dbab203be85c4ef427f","tid":1121710,"uid":3297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdabff7fbf92478b5b679ecb94baf3fc67acea50","tid":1121710,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"其實點解要認？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:26:42.000Z","msg":"幫其他組織掩飾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5df1d91fbeca4939e9c8e34d118c2b8c8c0841f","tid":1121710,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">紐西蘭基督城(Christchurch)2座清真寺遭到白人至上主義者攻擊的事件。</span><br />\n咁你去斯理蘭卡做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通金仔屌我老母<br />\n我去日本屌安培老母？"},{"pid":"929f56acb96feaae6381918ba15172a29eae836a","tid":1121710,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dis